# =============================================================================
# Scriberr Transcription Service Configuration
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authentication (OPTIONAL)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# You can pre-configure admin credentials if desired
# If not set, Scriberr will prompt you to create an account on first access
# SCRIBERR_USERNAME=admin
# SCRIBERR_PASSWORD=your-secure-password

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Upload Limits (OPTIONAL)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Maximum file size for uploads (default: 10GB)
# Increase if you need to process very large video files
BODY_SIZE_LIMIT=10G

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Service Information
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Access URL: http://scriberr.localhost
#
# Features:
# - Automatic audio/video transcription
# - Supports multiple file formats (MP3, MP4, WAV, etc.)
# - Web-based interface for upload and management
# - Whisper-based transcription engine
# - CPU-based processing (no GPU required on macOS)
#
# Note: macOS Compatibility
# - NVIDIA runtime removed (not available on macOS)
# - Transcription runs on CPU
# - Performance may be slower than GPU-accelerated version
# - For faster transcription, consider using smaller audio files
#
# Supported Formats:
# - Audio: MP3, WAV, FLAC, M4A, OGG
# - Video: MP4, AVI, MKV, MOV, WebM
#
# Use Cases:
# - Podcast transcription
# - Meeting recordings
# - Video content transcription
# - Interview transcription
# - Accessibility (generating captions)
#
# Technical Details:
# - Uses OpenAI Whisper model
# - SQLite database for metadata
# - Stores transcriptions in ./data directory
